national-campaign-crowdfunding-project%2F%3Fshow_desktop%3D1&d=qY%2BFdmg29Nq5PZFqoXGv4cjT01h1KCp2%2Bw2KB0oDRGE%3D&h=3a92271c\" target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9C%BE%E5%BF%97%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E7%9C%BE%E7%B1%8C%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project/?show_desktop=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>二、輿論戰線：</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">香港民主運動和抗爭，不斷受到中國造遙抹黑；中國媒體、英文五毛、投共白人，不斷在網上製造不利香港的輿論。為了令香港人不被代表、為了令外界清楚知道香港清晰的民意；</span><br />\n<strong>香港需要一份科學、具公信力的民調來反映真相。請支持：</strong><br />\n<strong><em><span style=\"color: orange;\">【我們香港人】倡導計劃</span></em></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.collaction.hk%2Fproject%2Fstory%2F1209&d=qY%2BFdmg29Nq5PZFqoXGv4cjT01h1KCp2%2Bw2KB0oDRGE%3D&h=c4cce868\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209</a>"},{"pid":"77494bbed58d8ce950ef792e4e36de20e494e743","tid":1678421,"uid":91767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2dedbec7d9a7b3a2c25f7c5c2390461efe0da6d3","tid":1678421,"uid":77012,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T08:43:23.000Z","msg":"靠食屎去打救"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T14:35:38.000Z","msg":"食夠三餐  份首期就儲夠"},{"pid":"44a5155bf0ae8948232e3224f561eead3b2a7531","tid":1678421,"uid":29093,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T14:43:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dWyoPuPfrGU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DdWyoPuPfrGU&d=qY%2BFdmg29Nq5PZFqoXGv4cjT01h1KCp2%2Bw2KB0oDRGE%3D&h=1cacbe0e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dWyoPuPfrGU</a><br />\n<br />\n諗起依首雨革歌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1064578358c5f8b14d32be679e7